          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p>By the end of this module, you will be able to:</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "list",
          "variant": "bulleted",
          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "list_style": "bulleted",
          "items_html": [
            "<p>Define the mechanical Canister substructure and vertical liquid cooling manifold integrations.</p>",
            "<p>Demonstrate the three phases of Pivoting Blind Mate Coupling engagement during node insertion. &nbsp;</p>",
            "<p>Compare real world implementations of the Helios architecture across hyperscale and enterprise partners.</p>",
            "<p>Anticipate upcoming data center macro trends, including extreme high voltage limits and optical interconnect scale.</p>"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "continue",
          "variant": "continue",
          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
